### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api

# Reemplaza estas variables con tus datos a medida que haces peticiones
@authToken = tu_token_aqui
@roomCode = codigo_de_la_sala_aqui
@roomId = uuid_de_la_sala_aqui

### ==================== AUTH MODULE ====================

### 1. Registrar un nuevo usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test2@example.com",
  "username": "testuser2",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Login (Obtener Token) -> Copia el token de la respuesta y ponlo en @authToken arriba
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test2@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Obtener tus datos (Requiere Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### ==================== MEDIA MODULE ====================

### 4. Validar una URL de video (Requiere Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/media/parse
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ"
}


### ==================== ROOMS MODULE ====================

### 5. Crear una sala (Requiere Token) -> Copia el "code" y ponlo en @roomCode arriba
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "Noche de pelis",
  "media_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ",
  "media_type": "YOUTUBE"
}

### 6. Ver todas las salas
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms

### 7. Buscar sala por código
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomCode}}

### 8. Unirse a una sala (Requiere Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomCode}}/join
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 9. Salir de la sala (Requiere Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomCode}}/leave
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 10. Eliminar sala (Solo el creador/host, Requiere Token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomCode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### ==================== CHAT MODULE ====================

### 11. Ver el historial de mensajes (Requiere el ID real de la sala, no el code. Requiere Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chats/{{roomId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
